{"tid":1232308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三罷不能停 民陣最新消息","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:32:14.000Z","uid":175623,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8280a4338e8d45290a259b7a395f66dd86e7a422","tid":1232308,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"【民陣聲明】<br />\nPress Statement - English Version Below<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線因應昨晚（6月15日）至今的最近形勢發出以下聲明：<br />\n<br />\n1. 民陣就昨日下午的記者會後，出現有關三罷資訊混亂向各位致歉。<br />\n<br />\n2. 民陣收到不少市民意見，感謝眾多市民在明天（6月17日）已作出三罷之準備，亦感謝各團體明天會於中環金鐘一帶繼續舉辦三罷活動，民陣會陸續將相關活動經社交媒體轉發，呼籲市民參加。<br />\n<br />\n3. 民陣明日上午9時到晚上7時，會於龍匯道一帶設立資訊站，讓市民到場與民陣交流運動方向，集思廣益。<br />\n<br />\n4. 民陣最後呼籲：全港市民不忘初心，今日下午兩時半到維園，參與民陣主辦黑衫大遊行，譴責鎮壓﹑撤回惡法﹑林鄭下台！<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019年6月16日<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nPress Statement<br />\nIn response to recent developments, Civil Human Rights Front (CHRF) makes the following statement:<br />\n<br />\n1. CHRF apologises for the confusion surrounding information about the general strike that came out after the press conference yesterday afternoon.<br />\n<br />\n2. CHRF has received many opinions from the public in this regard. The Front would like to show our gratitude to the many Hongkongers for their preparation to strike in Central and Admiralty. The Front will forward the related information on our social media platform and call for participation.<br />\n<br />\n3. CHRF will set up an information booth at Lung Wui Road from 9 am to 7 pm tomorrow. All are welcome to come discuss the possible future directions for the movement. <br />\n<br />\n4. CHRF reiterates: join our Black March today from Victoria Park, condemn the crackdown, withdraw the evil law, Carrie Lam, step down!<br />\n<br />\nCivil Human Rights Front<br />\n16 June 2019<br />\n［img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/BDRoGXZ.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDRoGXZ.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPg%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=56203077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/BDRoGXZ.png[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"dcdb93c523dfdd5b2149d012349c4ca3614534dd","tid":1232308,"uid":175623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1c0s8Dp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1c0s8Dp.png&h=8a20ac35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1653c57f402ba675d48e089813c069d00f41091","tid":1232308,"uid":24714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9b13ec659e2e69070590a792e3f4d2f7169fbfb","tid":1232308,"uid":24714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d071ec0583abda2aa12380abbe7586c04b3958aa","tid":1232308,"uid":24714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:11:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"029d5b3a9167b249da254c277426c8a2b4a91ee0","tid":1232308,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ea7bebc0568e7fe88dffc53d737e5e16fcb8f778","tid":1232308,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7c160d818a8689614e2172f981466d6debc1e00","tid":1232308,"uid":241363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"請廣傳<br />\n要斷續發酵事件<br />\n71慶回歸要拎雜種冇面<br />\n下屆建制就gg<br />\n2百萬要去盡佢<br />\n唔可以就咁算<br />\n林鄭下唔下台冇所謂<br />\n反正佢都冇晒管治威信<br />\n<br />\n1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 釋放不追究69/612被捕人士<br />\n3. 警察濫權要全面調查/受審<br />\n4. 平反612<br />\n5. 鄭若驊/李家超/盧偉聰問責下台"},{"pid":"0de2844d505933f4dc6bdd2e59fb4f36e696d02a","tid":1232308,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"813f6afa42aed6f5e5463eb970fd8f4e3da93ff6","tid":1232308,"uid":23560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"